"sc-gvZzpm eSvBWp pf-18_"><p class="sc-dycZeM hGxKPR pf-19_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-dQEsWe LHlFs pf-21_">Image by vetre via Envato Elements</span></p></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-aefb" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-fulBNO dOpZdJ pf-22_"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-dNsUpz hzCXJT"><div class="sc-jEABJj givtUl pf-23_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:8px;--s-sm:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gvZzpm eSvBWp pf-24_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-EgOky kRKCTs pf-25_">Veganuary 2025: A plant-powered start to the new year
</h3><p class="sc-dlWDvs hPuvxI pf-27_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-fb5b1a15-ecbe-4a16-900f-61bf8722103b"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">As we welcome the new year, Veganuary 2025 invites individuals worldwide to embrace a plant-based lifestyle for 31 days and experience its positive impact on their health, the planet, and animal welfare. This annual challenge has gained global momentum since its inception in 2014, inspiring millions to explore a vegan diet and fostering a growing community of environmentally conscious individuals.
</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-jEABJj givtUl pf-30_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gvZzpm eSvBWp pf-31_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-EgOky kRKCTs pf-32_">What is Veganuary?</h3><p class="sc-dlWDvs hPuvxI pf-34_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-5608cd3c-f067-4efb-9f98-704e3482ba6e"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">Veganuary is a non-profit organisation and global movement that encourages people to try veganism for January. The campaign aims to make the transition to a plant-based lifestyle simple and achievable by providing resources such as meal plans, recipes, and guidance.
</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-jEABJj givtUl pf-37_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gvZzpm eSvBWp pf-38_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-EgOky kRKCTs pf-39_">Key facts and statistics</h3><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-fThTNe kChLHI pf-41_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-SrAaV esjcyJ pf-42_">Since its inception in 2014, over 2 million people have officially signed up for the Veganuary challenge, with many more participating unofficially <u>(<a href="https://veganuary.com" target="_blank"><em><span style="color: rgb(74, 144, 226);"></span></em><span style="color: rgb(74, 144, 226);"></span></a></u><a href="https://veganuary.com" target="_blank"><span style="color: rgb(74, 144, 226);"></span></a><em><a href="https://veganuary.com" target="_blank"><span style="color: rgb(74, 144, 226);">Veganuary Annual Rep</span></a><a href="https://veganuary.com" target="_blank"><span style="color: rgb(74, 144, 226);">ort, 2024</span></a></em><a href="https://veganuary.com" target="_blank"><span style="color: rgb(74, 144, 226);"></span></a><a href="https://veganuary.com" target="_blank"><span style="color: rgb(74, 144, 226);"></span></a>).
</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-SrAaV esjcyJ pf-44_">During previous Veganuary campaigns, sales of plant-based food products increased by up to 25% in key markets as consumers explored new vegan options (<a href="https://www.statista.com" target="_blank"><span style="color: rgb(74, 144, 226);"></span></a><a href="https://www.statista.com" target="_blank"><span style="color: rgb(74, 144, 226);"><em>Market Research Report, 2024</em></span></a>).</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-SrAaV esjcyJ pf-46_"><span style="color: rgb(74, 144, 226);"></span>Participants in 2024 helped save the equivalent of 2.4 million kilograms of CO2 - the same as driving 6 million miles in an average car (<a href="https://veganuary.com" target="_blank"><span style="color: rgb(74, 144, 226);"><em>Veganuary Impact Stats</em></span></a>).
</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-SrAaV esjcyJ pf-48_"><a href="https://www.animalwelfare.org" target="_blank"></a>The 2024 campaign reported that each participant saved an estimated 10 animal lives by choosing plant-based foods throughout the month (<span style="color: rgb(74, 144, 226);"><a href="https://www.animalwelfare.org" target="_blank"><span style="color: rgb(74, 144, 226);"><em>Animal Welfare Report</em></span></a></span>).
</li></ul></div></div></div><div class="sc-jEABJj givtUl pf-50_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gvZzpm eSvBWp pf-51_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-EgOky kRKCTs pf-52_">The mission of Veganuary 2025</h3><p class="sc-dlWDvs hPuvxI pf-54_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-cb5357f9-8c36-4ae6-ad7a-6963f6053a32"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">This year, the overarching mission remains to support individuals in making sustainable lifestyle changes while raising awareness about the benefits of veganism. Although a specific theme for 2025 has not been announced, the campaign’s focus continues to highlight key issues such as health improvement, environmental sustainability, and ethical food choices.
</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-jEABJj givtUl pf-57_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gvZzpm eSvBWp pf-58_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-EgOky kRKCTs pf-59_">Why participate in Veganuary?
</h3><p class="sc-dlWDvs hPuvxI pf-61_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-8328572e-9c6e-45a0-bb2a-6ba5f67b2823"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">Participating in Veganuary is not only a personal challenge but also a chance to contribute to a global movement that is making a significant impact. Here are a few reasons why people across the globe join:</span></p><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-fThTNe kChLHI pf-64_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-SrAaV esjcyJ pf-65_"><strong>Health benefits </strong>- A plant-based diet can reduce the risk of chronic illnesses such as heart disease, diabetes, and high cholesterol. Many participants report increased energy levels, better digestion, and overall improved well-being.
</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-SrAaV esjcyJ pf-67_"><strong>Environmental impact</strong> - The production of plant-based foods typically requires fewer resources and produces lower carbon emissions compared to animal-based foods. By adopting a vegan diet, participants contribute to the reduction of their carbon footprint.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-SrAaV esjcyJ pf-69_"><strong>Animal welfare</strong> - Veganuary raises awareness about the conditions animals face in the meat and dairy industries, encouraging individuals to make compassionate choices.
</li></ul></div></div></div><div class="sc-jEABJj givtUl pf-71_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gvZzpm eSvBWp pf-72_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-EgOky kRKCTs pf-73_">How to get involved
</h3><p class="sc-dlWDvs hPuvxI pf-75_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-707db781-2c14-4667-a484-20b65fbda782"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">Whether you are new to veganism or looking to recommit to a plant-based lifestyle, there are numerous ways to participate in Veganuary 2025:</span></p><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-fThTNe kChLHI pf-78_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-SrAaV esjcyJ pf-79_"><strong>Sign up for the Veganuary pledge </strong>- Visit the official <em><a href="https://veganuary.com" target="_blank"><span style="color: rgb(74, 144, 226);"></span></a></em><a href="https://veganuary.com" target="_blank"><span style="color: rgb(74, 144, 226);"><em>Veganuary website</em></span></a> to sign up for free resources, including meal plans, nutritional tips, and recipes.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-SrAaV esjcyJ pf-81_"><strong>Follow the journey on social media</strong> - Engage with the Veganuary community on social media for support, inspiration, and recipe ideas.
</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-SrAaV esjcyJ pf-83_"><strong>Share your progress</strong> - Inspire others by sharing your plant-based journey through social media posts or discussions with family and friends.
</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-SrAaV esjcyJ pf-85_"><strong>Explore new foods</strong> - Use this opportunity to discover new vegan products, restaurants, and brands that align with your lifestyle.
</li></ul></div></div></div><div class="sc-jEABJj givtUl pf-87_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gvZzpm eSvBWp pf-88_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-EgOky kRKCTs pf-89_">Key highlights of Veganuary 2025
</h3><p class="sc-dlWDvs hPuvxI pf-91_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-c84754ab-21f5-4de6-ada1-4f29d616a121"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">Every year, Veganuary collaborates with influential figures, chefs, and celebrities to spread the message of plant-based living. In 2025, the campaign will feature exclusive recipes, motivational stories, and partnerships with major retailers to promote vegan-friendly products.
</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-jEABJj givtUl pf-94_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gvZzpm eSvBWp pf-95_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-EgOky kRKCTs pf-96_">Tips for a successful Veganuary</h3><p class="sc-dlWDvs hPuvxI pf-98_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-ba39fd07-471d-447c-bdfe-3e5881c2a631"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">Transitioning to a vegan lifestyle can be seamless with the right approach. Here are some practical tips to make your Veganuary experience enjoyable and rewarding:
</span></p><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-fThTNe kChLHI pf-101_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-SrAaV esjcyJ pf-102_"><strong>Plan your meals </strong>- Preparing your meals in advance can help you stay on track and avoid last-minute non-vegan choices.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-SrAaV esjcyJ pf-104_"><strong>Stock your pantry</strong> - Keep your kitchen stocked with essential vegan staples such as legumes, grains, fruits, and plant-based milk.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-SrAaV esjcyJ pf-106_"><strong>Try vegan versions of your favourite dishes</strong> - Many traditional recipes can be easily adapted using plant-based alternatives.
</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-SrAaV esjcyJ pf-108_"><strong>Stay informed</strong> - Read labels carefully to ensure products are vegan-friendly, and learn about common ingredients to avoid.
</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-SrAaV esjcyJ pf-110_"><strong>Be kind to yourself</strong> - It’s okay to make mistakes along the way. Every small change contributes to a larger impact.
</li></ul></div></div></div><div class="sc-jEABJj givtUl pf-112_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gvZzpm eSvBWp pf-113_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-EgOky kRKCTs pf-114_">The impact of Veganuary
</h3><p class="sc-dlWDvs hPuvxI pf-116_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-a7bc1605-b07c-48f8-932c-f48458b9afc1"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">The influence of Veganuary extends beyond January, with many participants continuing to incorporate plant-based habits into their daily lives. According to previous campaign data:
</span></p><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-fThTNe kChLHI pf-119_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-SrAaV esjcyJ pf-120_">Millions of people have participated globally, with many choosing to maintain a vegan lifestyle after the challenge.
</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-SrAaV esjcyJ pf-122_">Major food brands and restaurants often release new vegan options during Veganuary to cater to the growing demand.
</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-SrAaV esjcyJ pf-124_">Increased awareness and support for plant-based living contribute to long-term environmental and ethical improvements.
</li></ul></div></div></div><div class="sc-jEABJj givtUl pf-126_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gvZzpm eSvBWp pf-127_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-EgOky kRKCTs pf-128_">Conclusion</h3><p class="sc-dlWDvs hPuvxI pf-130_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-cd00588d-f78f-4eac-92e3-73608e3a91e0"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">Veganuary 2025 is more than just a challenge - it’s an opportunity to embrace a lifestyle that aligns with health, sustainability, and compassion. Whether you’re aiming to make a permanent change or simply want to try something new, participating in Veganuary can be a transformative experience. By taking the pledge and sharing your journey, you become part of a global movement that’s reshaping the future of food.<br><br>Make this January a month of discovery, mindful habits, and impactful positive change. Join Veganuary 2025 and take your first step towards a healthier lifestyle and a thriving planet. Whether you're starting your plant-based journey for personal wellness or aiming to promote healthy habits in your workplace. <a href="https://www.mandatorytraining.co.uk/pages/online-cpd-courses-training-cpd-accredited-elearning-courses" target="_blank"><em><span style="color: rgb(74, 144, 226);"></span></em></a><em><a href="https://www.mandatorytraining.co.uk/" target="_blank"></a></em><a href="https://www.mandatorytraining.co.uk/" target="_blank"><a href="https://www.mandatorytraining.co.uk/" target="_blank"><em><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="color: rgb(74, 144, 226);">The Mandatory Training Group</span></span></em></a></a> provide actionable guidance to help you succeed. For organisations, the <a href="https://www.mandatorytraining.co.uk/pages/complyplus-cqc-compliance-system" target="_blank"><em><span style="color: rgb(74, 144, 226);">ComplyPlus™</span></em></a> off